headline: NiSource (NYSE:NI) Has Announced That It Will Be Increasing Its Dividend To $0.30
summary: The board of NiSource Inc. ( NYSE:NI ) has announced that the dividend on 20th of February will be increased to $0.30...

headline: MISO regulators seek stakeholder review for DOE ‘emergency’ orders cost allocation
summary: The U.S. Department of Energy has failed to show there are reliability benefits from keeping power plants from retiring in the Midcontinent region, state utility regulators told FERC.
